\measuredangle
a,b,c
m=a+\alpha(c-a)
n=c+\alpha(b-c)
o=\frac{a+b}2
\alpha=\frac{1+i}2
 m-o = i(n-o)
m-o = -\frac i2a-\frac12 b+\frac{1+i}2c
n-o = -\frac 12a+\frac i2 b+\frac{1-i}2c
